  "detailed_description": "Unformed is one of the most Souls-like Metroidvania 2D horizontal ARPG. Players will explore the eastern dark world, seeking the astonishing truth behind the unspeakable mysterious events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b87d4f452c75c7857055532a18f91a4e.poster.avif?t=1616667504\" width=650 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b87d4f452c75c7857055532a18f91a4e.webm?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b87d4f452c75c7857055532a18f91a4e.mp4?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Dark Souls</i> series (include <i>Bloodborne</i> and <i>Sekiro</i>) are always our studio's favorite, and developing our own soul-like game has been our target since the studio established. Every single player has his/her own understanding about what the most \"soul-like\" factors are in games, and our game, <i>Unformed</i> is the our studio's first answer sheet. Perhaps there would be no fancy special effects nor eye-dizzying battles, but we do hope players could experience the tesion of exploring dangerous stages and the accomplishment of beating invincible enemies just like they did in <i>Dark Souls</i> series, and enjoy our spooky eastern myths story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/bba82b4a658ff9e0f010fd905861e709.poster.avif?t=1616667504\" width=650 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/bba82b4a658ff9e0f010fd905861e709.webm?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/bba82b4a658ff9e0f010fd905861e709.mp4?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Our game, Unformed is still in early access stage. In the next one year and a half we will keep polishing the current existing content and publishing new content such as stages / enemies / stories etc. Also we will communicate with players on Steam about our developing plan. If any bugs / mistakes happen in our game, please let us know by leaving comment on Steam, we will react as fast as we can.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b8e60f5021068de4c127191517dea03c.poster.avif?t=1616667504\" width=650 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b8e60f5021068de4c127191517dea03c.webm?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b8e60f5021068de4c127191517dea03c.mp4?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Unformed is one of the most Souls-like Metroidvania 2D horizontal ARPG. Players will explore the eastern dark world, seeking the astonishing truth behind the unspeakable mysterious events.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b87d4f452c75c7857055532a18f91a4e.poster.avif?t=1616667504\" width=650 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b87d4f452c75c7857055532a18f91a4e.webm?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b87d4f452c75c7857055532a18f91a4e.mp4?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Dark Souls</i> series (include <i>Bloodborne</i> and <i>Sekiro</i>) are always our studio's favorite, and developing our own soul-like game has been our target since the studio established. Every single player has his/her own understanding about what the most \"soul-like\" factors are in games, and our game, <i>Unformed</i> is the our studio's first answer sheet. Perhaps there would be no fancy special effects nor eye-dizzying battles, but we do hope players could experience the tesion of exploring dangerous stages and the accomplishment of beating invincible enemies just like they did in <i>Dark Souls</i> series, and enjoy our spooky eastern myths story.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/bba82b4a658ff9e0f010fd905861e709.poster.avif?t=1616667504\" width=650 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/bba82b4a658ff9e0f010fd905861e709.webm?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/bba82b4a658ff9e0f010fd905861e709.mp4?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Our game, Unformed is still in early access stage. In the next one year and a half we will keep polishing the current existing content and publishing new content such as stages / enemies / stories etc. Also we will communicate with players on Steam about our developing plan. If any bugs / mistakes happen in our game, please let us know by leaving comment on Steam, we will react as fast as we can.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b8e60f5021068de4c127191517dea03c.poster.avif?t=1616667504\" width=650 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b8e60f5021068de4c127191517dea03c.webm?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/674480/extras/b8e60f5021068de4c127191517dea03c.mp4?t=1616667504\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
